HEADWORD: Unnecessary
<hw>Un*nec"es*sa*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not necessary;
not required under the circumstances; unless; needless; <as>as,
<ex>unnecessary</ex> labor, care, or rigor</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*nec"es*sa*ri*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*nec"es*sa*ri*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

